---
title: American-Style Steak & Mustard Sauce with Creamy Onion Mash
description: Long after you finish this dinner of steak and three veg, you're going to remember the way it was transformed by the simple addition
of a luscious mustard sauce. It's an easy trick that gives this classic dish a new lease of life.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/american-beef-rump-mustard-sauce-90f17935.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/american-style-steak-mustard-sauce-616919aa985156020f726dc6-68f387dc.pdf
time required: 40 minutes
cuisine: North America
